Exercise 1: Calculation of the absorption spectrum of benzene molecule (C6H6) using
            the Independent Particle Approximation

 Step 1. Run the SCF ground-state calculation

    mpirun -np 2 /scratch/timrov/QE_tmp7_6.0/qe-6.0/bin/pw.x < Benzene.scf.in > Benzene.scf.out

 Step 2. Run the spectrum calculation

    mpirun -np 2 /scratch/timrov/QE_tmp7_6.0/qe-6.0/bin/epsilon.x < Benzene.epsilon.in > Benzene.epsilon.out 

 Step 3. Plot the spectrum using "gnuplot" and the script "plot_spectrum.gnu":

    gnuplot -> load 'plot_spectrum.gnu'

    evince Benzene_spectrum.eps
